{"tid":641603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女警萬寧偷$1.3萬護膚品　待精神報告押後訊","createTime":"2018-04-25T06:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T07:44:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"470cf2ab112ae5c8b667cbbdb788792e82518304","tid":641603,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180425/photo/bkn-20180425133344617-0425_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180425141856\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180425%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180425133344617-0425_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180425141856&h=33cb39f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n22歲女警涉在3間萬寧內，4度偷取護膚產品，總值逾1.3萬港元。她事後被控4項盜竊罪，今(25日)在九龍城法院提訊。女警暫毋須答辯，案件押後至6月20日再訊，期間准繼續保釋。 <br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告李慧玲於今年2月15日至3月9日，在青衣城、旺角新世紀廣場和九龍灣德福商場的萬寧內，合共偷取29件護膚品。 <br />\n<br />\n控方指已準備答辯，但辯方指需時索取文件，以及取得精神科報告，並透露被告曾向葵涌醫院精神科門診求醫，因此申請押後審訊，獲裁判官批准。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180425/bkn-20180425133344617-0425_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180425%2Fbkn-20180425133344617-0425_00822_001.html&d=mamiB8kKqeBR%2BeAuePE5xDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=feb552e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180425/bkn-20180425133344617-0425_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"eda98d2e10391087f9c9089fede366c2ce1f7432","tid":641603,"uid":31355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"休班警無惡不作"},{"pid":"0f750cc2bcd3a5f5017b4aa49a7d33d3102026a2","tid":641603,"uid":142854,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T06:35:40.000Z","msg":"Madam偷野唔洗你教"},{"pid":"73546dab9b4f990b0edce601e72878805c8b6fa8","tid":641603,"uid":18385,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T06:38:46.000Z","msg":"屌你我入黎係睇最後果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"